<!ELEMENT Library (book+, author+, publisher+)>
<!ELEMENT book (title, price, year)>
<!ATTLIST book ISBN ID #REQUIRED writtenby IDREFS #IMPLIED publishedby IDREF #IMPLIED>
<!ELEMENT title (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT price (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT year (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT author (address, URL)>
<!ATTLIST author name ID #REQUIRED bookswritten IDREFS #IMPLIED>
<!ELEMENT address (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT URL (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT publisher (address, phone, URL)>
<!ATTLIST publisher name ID #REQUIRED bookspublished IDREFS #IMPLIED>
<!ELEMENT phone (#PCDATA)>